                     <list>
                        <item xml:id="a1">
                           <locus/><p>&#160;<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;">Fol. 1v: Purchase note.</span></p> <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"></span></p><q xml:lang="gez"><p><span style="font-size: small;"><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Fol. 1v:</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:&#10;115%;font-family:"> </span><span style="font-size: large;"><span lang="AMH" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: Nyala;">&#4824;&#4637;&#4637;&#4653;&#4961;</span></span><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">[sic]</span></span><span style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"> </span><span style="font-size: large;"><span lang="AMH" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: Nyala;">&#4872;&#4709;&#4648;&#4961;</span><span lang="AMH" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"> </span><span lang="AMH" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: Nyala;">&#4632;&#4853;&#4736;&#4757;&#4961;</span><span lang="AMH" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"> </span><span lang="AMH" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: Nyala;">&#4632;&#4925;&#4624;&#4941;&#4961;</span><span lang="AMH" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"> </span><span lang="AMH" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: Nyala;">&#4658;&#4872;&#4827;&#4961;</span><span lang="AMH" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"> </span><span lang="AMH" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: Nyala;">&#4632;&#4637;&#4613;&#4653;&#4961;</span><span lang="AMH" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"> </span><span lang="AMH" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: Nyala;">&#4656;&#4709;&#4624;&#4725;&#4961; &#4616;&#4768;&#4709;&#4961; &#4808;&#4621;&#4848;&#4961; &#4768;&#4706;&#4840;&#4961; &#4768;&#4901;&#4673;&#4961; &#4872;&#4709;&#4648;&#4961; &#4634;&#4779;&#4772;&#4621;&#4961; &#4632;&#4829;&#4633;&#4653;&#4961; &#4752;&#4704;&#4649;&#4961; &#4840;&#4720;&#4872;&#4827;&#4961; &#4704;&#4978;&#4961; &#4709;&#4653;&#4961; &#4752;&#4813;</span></span></p></q>
                           <q xml:lang="en"/>
                           <p>The note is written in Amharic in a crude hand. The price of the book is indicated as 10 Bǝrr.</p>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a2">
                           <locus/><p>&#160;<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;">Fol. 2ra-rc: Inventory of land possessions of D&#228;br&#228; Dammo.</span></p> <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:" unicode=""></span></p><q xml:lang="gez"><p><span style="font-size: small;">&#160;<span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 115%;" unicode="">Fol. 2ra:</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:&#10;115%;font-family:" unicode=""> </span><span style="font-size: large;"><span lang="AMH" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: Nyala;">&#4742;&#4621;&#4680;&#4961; &#4872;&#4651;&#4813;&#4629;&#4961; &#4824;&#4848;&#4709;&#4648;&#4961; &#4851;&#4638;&#4961;</span></span><span lang="AMH" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&#10;Nyala;mso-fareast-font-family:" arial="" unicode=""> </span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:115%;&#10;font-family:" unicode="">&#8230;</span></p></q>
                           <q xml:lang="en"/>
                           <p>The note is written in the same hand as Additio 1.</p>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a3">
                           <locus/><p>&#160;<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;">Fol. 2vb, ls. 1-11: Inventory of items.</span></p> <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:" unicode=""></span></p><q xml:lang="gez"><p>&#160;<span style="font-size: small;"><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Fol. 2vb, ls. 1-3:</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:&#10;115%;font-family:" unicode=""> </span><span style="font-size: large;"><span lang="AMH" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: Nyala;">&#4749;&#4621;&#4680;&#4961; &#4757;&#4811;&#4843;&#4725;&#4961; &#4824;&#4720;&#4744;&#4616;&#4680;&#4961; &#4704;&#4642;&#4632;&#4720;&#4961; &#4632;&#4637;&#4613;&#4653;&#4961; &#4675;&#4616;&#4961; &#4768;&#4709;</span></span><span style="font-size: large;"><span lang="AMH" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: Nyala;">&#4961;</span></span><span lang="AMH" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:115%;&#10;font-family:Nyala;mso-fareast-font-family:" arial="" unicode=""> </span><span style="font-size:10.0pt;&#10;line-height:115%;font-family:" unicode="">&#8230;</span></p></q>
                           <q xml:lang="en"/>
                           <p>The note was drawn up during the tenure of abbot (mämhǝr) Qalä ʾAb. It aso mentions mämhǝr Wäldä Arägawi.</p>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a4">
                           <locus/><p>&#160;<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;">Fol. 2vb, ls. 12-32: Inventory of items.</span></p> <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:" unicode=""></span></p><q xml:lang="gez"><p><span style="font-size: small;">&#160;<span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 115%;" unicode="">Fol. 2vb, ls. 12-14:</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:&#10;115%;font-family:" unicode=""> </span><span style="font-size: large;"><span lang="AMH" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: Nyala;">&#4749;&#4621;&#4680;&#4961; &#4757;&#4811;&#4843;&#4725;&#4961; &#4824;&#4720;&#4744;&#4616;&#4680;&#4961; &#4704;&#4642;&#4632;&#4720;&#4961; &#4632;&#4637;&#4613;&#4653;&#4961; &#4872;&#4709;&#4648;&#4961; &#4768;&#4648;&#4875;&#4810;&#4961;</span></span><span lang="AMH" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:115%;&#10;font-family:Nyala;mso-fareast-font-family:" arial="" unicode=""> </span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:&#10;10.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:" unicode="">&#8230;</span></p></q>
                           <q xml:lang="en"/>
                           <p>The note is written in Gǝʿǝz and Amharic. It was drawn up during the tenure of abbot (mämhǝr) Gäbrä ʾArägawi and lists paraphernalia and the general number of books. It also mentions qes gäbäz Täsfa Śǝllase and qes Gäbrä Maryam.</p>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a5">
                           <locus/><p>&#160;<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;">Fol. 2vc: Land transaction note.</span></p> <p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt;" class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" unicode="" style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"></span></p><q xml:lang="gez"><p><span style="font-size: small;">&#160;<span lang="EN-US" unicode="" style="line-height: 115%;">Fol. 2vc:</span></span><span lang="EN-US" unicode="" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:&#10;115%;font-family:"> </span><span style="font-size: large;"><span lang="AMH" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: Nyala;">&#4843;&#4726;: &#4872;&#4853;&#4617;&#4961; &#4650;&#4637;&#4961; &#4840;&#4752;&#4704;&#4651;&#4961; &#4708;&#4720;&#4961; &#4846;&#4624;&#4757;&#4661;&#4961; &#4720;&#4643;&#4840;&#4901;&#4777;&#4961; &#4768;&#4752;&#4961; &#4621;&#4869;&#4961; &#4768;&#4707;&#4845;&#4961; &#4773;&#4637;&#4768;&#4726;&#4961; &#4872;&#4853;&#4617;&#4961; &#4773;&#4757;&#4853;&#4653;&#4843;&#4661;&#4961; &#4704;&#4972;&#4709;&#4653;&#4961; &#4616;&#4811;&#4755;&#4962;</span></span><span lang="AMH" unicode="" arial="" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&#10;Nyala;mso-fareast-font-family:"> </span><span lang="EN-GB" unicode="" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:">&#8230;</span></p></q>
                           <q xml:lang="en"/>
                           <p>The note is written in Gǝʿǝz and Amharic. Its states that lǝǧ ʾAbbay purchased a rim-land from ʾato Gädlu ʾƎndrǝyas; it also mentions several individuals as witnesses, nǝburä ʾǝd Wäldä Giyorgis and King Yoḥannǝs IV.</p>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a6">
                           <locus/><p>&#160;<span style="font-size: small;"><span lang="EN-US" unicode="" style="line-height: 115%;">Fol. 136va-vb: Inventory of items and books.</span></span></p><q xml:lang="gez"/>
                           <q xml:lang="en"/>
                           <p>The note is written in a mediocre hand. It was drawn up during the tenure of abbot (mämhǝr) Täklä Giyorgis and lists paraphernalia and books with their quantity. It also mentions qesä gäbäz Wäldä ʾAlfa, qesä gäbäz Gäbrä ʾArägawi and ʾafä gäbäz Gäbrä Krǝstos.</p>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a7">
                           <locus/><p>&#160;<span lang="EN-GB" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Fol. 136vb, ls. 13-27: Land grant issued by </span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">ras M&#228;ng&#228;&#353;a for D&#228;br&#228; Maryam (?).</span></p> <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt;"><span lang="EN-GB" style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:" unicode=""></span></p><q xml:lang="gez"><p>&#160;<span lang="EN-GB" unicode="" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:&#10;115%;font-family:">Fol. 136vb, ls. 13-17: </span><span style="font-size: large;"><span lang="AMH" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: Nyala;">&#4845;&#4708;&#4961;</span><span lang="AMH" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"> </span><span lang="AMH" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: Nyala;">&#4651;&#4661;&#4961;</span><span lang="AMH" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"> </span><span lang="AMH" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: Nyala;">&#4632;&#4757;&#4872;&#4667;&#4961;</span><span lang="AMH" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"> </span><span lang="AMH" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: Nyala;">&#4808;&#4621;&#4848;&#4961;</span><span lang="AMH" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"> </span><span lang="AMH" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: Nyala;">&#4757;&#4873;&#4640;&#4961;</span><span lang="AMH" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"> </span><span lang="AMH" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: Nyala;">&#4752;&#4872;&#4645;&#4725;&#4961;</span><span lang="AMH" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"> </span><span lang="AMH" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: Nyala;">&#4846;&#4624;&#4757;&#4661;&#4961;</span><span lang="AMH" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"> </span><span lang="AMH" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: Nyala;">&#4808;&#4624;&#4709;&#4777;&#4961;</span><span lang="AMH" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"> </span><span lang="AMH" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: Nyala;">&#4637;&#4853;&#4648;&#4961;</span><span lang="AMH" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"> </span><span lang="AMH" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: Nyala;">&#4768;&#4877;&#4768;&#4961; &#4901;&#4653;&#4676;&#4961; &#4616;&#4848;&#4709;&#4648;&#4961; &#4635;&#4653;&#4843;&#4637;&#4961;</span></span><span lang="AMH" unicode="" arial="" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:Nyala;mso-fareast-font-family:&#10;"> </span><span lang="EN-GB" unicode="" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:">&#8230;</span></p></q>
                           <q xml:lang="en"/>
                           <p>The note states that ras Mängäša (1868-1906), son of King Yoḥannǝs IV, donated a land property to Däbrä Maryam.</p>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a8">
                           <locus/><p><span style="font-size: small;">&#160;<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Fol. 136vc, ls. 1-25: Inventory of books and items.</span></span></p> <p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt;" class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" unicode="" style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"></span></p><q xml:lang="gez"><p>&#160;<span style="font-size: small;"><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 115%;" unicode="">Fol. 136vc, ls. 1-5:</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:&#10;115%;font-family:" unicode=""> </span><span style="font-size: large;"><span lang="AMH" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: Nyala;">&#4748;&#4621;&#4672;&#4961; </span></span><span lang="AMH" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: Nyala;">[</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">sic]</span><span style="font-size: large;"><span lang="AMH" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: Nyala;">&#160;&#4632;&#4923;&#4629;&#4941;&#4725;&#4961; &#4984;&#4976;&#4721;&#4961; &#4748;&#4621;&#4672;&#4961; &#4661;&#4843;&#4851;&#4961; &#4982;&#4970;&#4725;&#4961; &#4748;&#4621;&#4672;&#4961; &#4877;&#4709;&#4648;&#4961; &#4632;&#4653;&#4941;&#4821;&#4961; &#4982;&#4974;&#4725;&#4961;</span></span><span lang="AMH" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:115%;&#10;font-family:Nyala;mso-fareast-font-family:" arial="" unicode=""> </span><span style="font-size:&#10;10.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:" unicode="">&#8230;</span></p></q>
                           <q xml:lang="en"/>
                           <p>The note was written in a mediocre hand during the reign of King Yoḥannǝs IV and the tenure of abbot (mämhǝr) Täklä Giyorgis. It also mentions ʾagbaz ʾabba Wäldä ʾAlfa and ʾabba Gäbrä ʾArägawi.</p>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a9">
                           <locus/><p>&#160;<span style="font-size: small;"><span lang="EN-US" unicode="" style="line-height: 115%;">Fol. 136vc, ls. 26-34: Inventory of items and books.</span></span></p><q xml:lang="gez"><p>&#160;<span style="font-size: small;"><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 115%;" unicode="">Fol. 136vc, ls. 26-29:</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:&#10;115%;font-family:" unicode=""> </span><span style="font-size: large;"><span lang="AMH" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: Nyala;">&#4749;&#4621;&#4680;&#4961; &#4637;&#4757;&#4923;&#4941;&#4961; &#4824;&#4661;&#4843;&#4851;&#4961; &#4982;&#4972;&#4961; &#4749;&#4621;&#4680;&#4961; &#4877;&#4637;&#4869;&#4961; &#4987;&#4978;&#4972;&#4961; &#4662;&#4651;&#4961; &#4983;&#4970;&#4961; &#4749;&#4621;&#4680;&#4961; &#4632;&#4923;&#4629;&#4941;&#4725;&#4961; &#4985;&#4970;&#4962;</span></span><span lang="AMH" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:" unicode=""> </span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;&#10;line-height:115%;font-family:" unicode="">&#8230;</span></p></q>
                           <q xml:lang="en"/>
                           <p>The note was drawn up during the tenure of abbot (mämhǝr) Wäldä ʿAbiy ʾƎgziʾ and lists paraphernalia and the general number of books. It also mentions qes gäbäz Gäbrä ʾIyäsus and qes gäbäz Wäldä ʿAbiy ʾƎgziʾ. Some letters are partly erased.</p>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a10">
                           <locus/><p>&#160;<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;">Fols. 137ra-138ra: History of D&#228;br&#228; Dammo.</span></p> <p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt;" class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" unicode="" style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"></span></p><q xml:lang="gez"><p><span style="font-size: small;">&#160;<span style="line-height: 115%;" unicode="">Fol. 137ra:</span></span><span style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:115%;&#10;font-family:" unicode=""> </span><span style="font-size: large;"><span lang="AMH" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: Nyala;">&#4757;&#4812;&#4901;&#4757;&#4961; &#4704;&#4648;&#4853;&#4772;&#4720;&#4961; &#4773;&#4877;&#4826;&#4768;&#4709;&#4628;&#4653;&#4961; &#4632;&#4925;&#4624;&#4936;&#4961; &#4723;&#4650;&#4781;&#4961; &#4824;&#4848;&#4709;&#4648;&#4961; &#4851;&#4638;&#4961; &#4632;&#4677;&#4848;&#4656;&#4961; &#4768;&#4707;&#4961; &#4768;&#4648;&#4875;&#4810;&#4961; &#4824;&#4776;&#4632;&#4961; &#4720;&#4752;&#4645;&#4720;&#4725;&#4961; &#4808;&#4720;&#4624;&#4757;&#4928;&#4725;&#4962;</span></span><span lang="AMH" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:115%;&#10;font-family:Nyala;mso-fareast-font-family:" arial="" unicode=""> </span><span style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:" unicode="">&#8230;</span></p></q>
                           <q xml:lang="en"><p>&#160;<span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:&#10;115%;font-family:" unicode="">Fol. 137ra: &#8220;We begin with the help of God the book of the Story of D&#228;br&#228; Dammo, sanctuary of &#704;abba &#704;Ar&#228;gawi, how it was destroyed and built &#8230;&#8221;&#160;</span></p></q>
                           <p>The note states that the sanctuary was destroyed by an earthquake during the first year of reign of King ʾIyasu III (= 1784 A.D.), 270 years after that king Lǝbnä Dǝngǝl had built it, and it was rebuilt thanks to däǧǧazmač Wäldä Gäbrǝʾel. The note also mentions other individuals: Zä-Giyorgis, Fǝśśǝḥa Ṣǝyon, ʾAnqäṣä Haymanot, etc. Nomina sacra (Maryam) and elements of Ethiopic numerals are rubricated.</p>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a11">
                           <locus/><p>&#160;<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;">Fol. 138ra-rb: Inventory of books and items.</span></p> <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:" unicode=""></span></p><q xml:lang="gez"><p><span style="font-size: small;">&#160;<span style="line-height: 115%;" unicode="">Fol. 138ra:</span></span><span style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:115%;&#10;font-family:" unicode=""> </span><span style="font-size: large;"><span lang="AMH" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: Nyala;">&#4749;&#4621;&#4680;&#4961;</span><span lang="AMH" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"> </span><span lang="AMH" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: Nyala;">&#4632;&#4923;&#4629;&#4941;&#4725;&#4961;</span><span lang="AMH" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"> </span><span lang="AMH" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: Nyala;">&#4969;&#4774;&#4650;&#4725;&#4961;</span><span lang="AMH" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"> </span><span lang="AMH" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: Nyala;">&#4624;&#4637;&#4661;&#4721;&#4961;</span><span lang="AMH" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"> </span><span lang="AMH" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: Nyala;">&#4661;&#4757;&#4781;&#4659;&#4653;&#4961;</span></span><span lang="AMH" style="font-size:10.0pt;&#10;line-height:115%;font-family:" unicode=""> </span><span style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:" unicode="">&#8230;</span></p></q>
                           <q xml:lang="en"/>
                           <p>The note is written in a crude hand. Series of dashes have been inserted above many items in the second part of the note.</p>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a12">
                           <locus/><p>&#160;<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;">Fol. 138rc, ls. 5-13: Inventory of items.</span></p> <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:" unicode=""></span></p><q xml:lang="gez"><p><span style="font-size: small;">&#160;<span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 115%;" unicode="">Fol. 138rc, ls. 5-8:</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:&#10;115%;font-family:" unicode=""> </span><span style="font-size: large;"><span lang="AMH" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: Nyala;">&#4749;&#4621;&#4685;&#4961; &#4757;&#4811;&#4843;&#4725;&#4961; &#4824;&#4720;&#4925;&#4629;&#4936;&#4961; &#4704;&#4824;&#4632;&#4752;&#4961; &#4632;&#4637;&#4613;&#4653;&#4961; &#4778;&#4851;&#4752;&#4961; &#4675;&#4621;&#4961;</span></span><span lang="AMH" style="font-size:10.0pt;&#10;line-height:115%;font-family:" unicode=""> </span><span style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:" unicode="">&#8230;</span></p></q>
                           <q xml:lang="en"/>
                           <p>The note was drawn up during the tenure of abbot (mämhǝr) Kidanä Qal.</p>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a13">
                           <locus/><p>&#160;<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;">Fol. 138rc, ls. 14-25: Inventory of items.</span></p> <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:" unicode=""></span></p><q xml:lang="gez"><p><span style="font-size: small;">&#160;<span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 115%;" unicode="">Fol. 138rc, ls. 14-18:</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:&#10;115%;font-family:" unicode=""> </span><span style="font-size: large;"><span lang="AMH" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: Nyala;">&#4749;&#4621;&#4680;&#4961; &#4757;&#4811;&#4843;&#4725;&#4961; &#4824;&#4708;&#4720;&#4961; &#4781;&#4653;&#4661;&#4722;&#4843;&#4757;&#4961; &#4824;&#4720;&#4744;&#4616;&#4680;&#4961; &#4704;&#4824;&#4632;&#4752;&#4961; &#4846;&#4624;&#4757;&#4661;&#4961; &#4704;&#4768;&#4707;&#4961; &#4661;&#4709;&#4624;&#4725;&#4961; &#4616;&#4768;&#4709;&#4961; &#4632;&#4637;&#4629;&#4653;&#4752;&#4725;&#4961;&#160;</span></span><span style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:" unicode="">&#8230;</span></p></q>
                           <q xml:lang="en"/>
                           <p>The note was drawn up during the reign of King Yoḥannǝs IV and the tenure of abbot (mämhǝr) Sǝbḥat lä-ʾAb. It also mentions ʾabba Näṣṣärä ʾAb and ʾabba Wäldä Ḥǝy(wä)t.</p>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e1">- The title ፍትሐ፡ ነገሥት፡ is written on the upper right margin of fol. 1r in modern blue pen. &#xD;
- Gǝʿǝz and Amharic comments are written in a secondary hand in a small script in the margins or in the intercolumns: e.g., fols. 10v, 28r, 29r, 34r, 36v, 73r, 76r.&#xD;
- Tämälläs-sign, in the shape of two perpendicular lines (˧ or ┴), indicating the place where the omissions, written in the margin, belong: fols. 11va, 13va, 15va, 20ra, 26va, 31va, 40rc, 53vc, 77ra.&#xD;
- Omitted letters or words inserted interlineally: e.g., fols. 4rb, 18ra, 36rc, 45rc, 70rc, 98rb.&#xD;
- Omitted letters or words added at the beginning of the line: fols. 66va, 95va, 122va.&#xD;
- Omitted letters or words added at the end of the line: fols. 9rc, 16rc, 49vb, 67va, 77ra.&#xD;
- Corrections written over erasures: fols. 3va, 6ra, 8ra, 9rb, 11va, 12va, 14ra, 14vc etc.&#xD;
- Erasures marked with thin black lines: e.g., fols. 3ra, 6rb, 55vc, 65vb, 73ra.&#xD;
- Erasure marked with a crude black line: fol. 16vc.&#xD;
- Immediate corrections indicated by thin frames in black ink around the word or the sentence: fols. 37vc, 44rb, 55vc, 60rb, 62rb, 62vc.&#xD;
- Pen trial: fols. 1r, 1v.&#xD;
- Illegible note in pencil on fol. 138vc.</item>
